          "description": "I\u2019ve been to many dental offices, and this is finally one I can say I\u2019ll be sticking with. The office feels small and personal (the receptionist knew who I was when I walked in), and I never felt rushed during my visit.\n\nMy dental hygienist, Kira, is the best I\u2019ve ever had. She took the time to listen, was incredibly gentle, and paid close attention to every detail. I especially appreciated how she explained what she was seeing as she worked. She was attentive, and you can tell she genuinely cares and is highly skilled at what she does.\n\nDr. Halary was also great. I\u2019ve been dealing with an ongoing dental issue, and she really heard me out and respected how I want to move forward, unlike others who have pushed for treatments I didn\u2019t want.\n\nI also respect that, unlike some other offices that offer incentives  in exchange for reviews, this office doesn\u2019t rely on that. Their reviews are genuine, which says a lot about the quality of care.",
