          "description": "Beautiful office, welcoming, sweet and great staff! The shortest time wait I\u2019ve ever had. The doctor saw the problem right away and fixed it! It was my first time receiving a dental procedure with a bite block and it was such a relieve.\nAnd also, I was given a tv remote to pick my own show to watch during the visit \u263a\ufe0f",
