          "description": "This was easily the best experience I\u2019ve ever had going to the dentist. The whole place was tastefully decorated and the staff was incredibly caring and straightforward about my copayments. I was there to get a second opinion because my previous dentist told me I needed to get eight cavities filled. Dr. Halary took the time to walk me through everything and assured me it was only three that actually needed immediate attention. Needless to say I will not be going back to my old dentist. Also they have a TV in the room and you can pick whatever you want on Netflix.",
