          "description": "Excellent experience from start to finish.\nDr. Halary and her team were incredibly thorough during my examination and cleaning, taking the time to explain everything clearly. The office runs efficiently with minimal waiting time and a very organized process. I left feeling well cared for and confident in the quality of their work. Highly recommended.\u201d",
