          "description": "I had an excellent experience with Dr. Halary and her entire staff. The office is very clean and modern, and I was especially impressed by the new standing X-ray machine\u2014it was quick and comfortable. Dr. Halary took the time to clearly explain my receded gum issue in a way that was easy to understand and made me feel at ease. My teeth cleaning went smoothly, and as a nice bonus, I even got a goodie bag afterward. The front desk staff was also fantastic\u2014they found my insurance information for me and offered to help submit a claim, which I happily accepted. Overall, a very professional, friendly, and thorough dental visit. Highly recommend! \ud83d\ude0a\ud83e\uddb7",
